.TH AGENT-HOOK-PROMPT-SUBMIT 1 "2026-06-30" "agentguard" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
agent-hook-prompt-submit \- handle prompt-time agent context refresh
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B agent-hook-prompt-submit
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B agent-hook-prompt-submit
reads a prompt-submit hook JSON payload from standard input and delegates
memory-intent reminders and prompt-time context refresh policy to
.BR "hm hook prompt-submit" .
It then resets once-per-prompt AgentGuard state used by edit and command
guidance.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B AGENTGUARD_HIVE_MEMORY_HOOKS
Set to
.B 0
to disable Hive Memory hook integration.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Prompt handling completed.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR hm (1),
.BR agent-hook-session-start (1)
